{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0181P21Yn6YC44Bqb9fywfx5","type":"tool_result","content":"    79→namespace E88\n    80→\n    81→open Real Matrix Finset BigOperators\n    82→\n    83→variable {d : ℕ} [NeZero d]  -- State dimension per head\n    84→\n    85→/-! ## Part 1: E88 Core Architecture -/\n    86→\n    87→/-- E88 single-head configuration -/\n    88→structure E88Head (inputDim headDim : ℕ) where\n    89→  /-- Decay/recurrence factor α ∈ (0, 2) -/\n    90→  α : ℝ\n    91→  /-- Input scaling δ -/\n    92→  δ : ℝ\n    93→  /-- Key projection matrix K: headDim × inputDim -/\n    94→  keyProj : Matrix (Fin headDim) (Fin inputDim) ℝ\n    95→  /-- Value projection matrix V: headDim × inputDim -/\n    96→  valueProj : Matrix (Fin headDim) (Fin inputDim) ℝ\n    97→  /-- Stability constraint on α -/\n    98→  α_bounds : 0 < α ∧ α < 2\n    99→\n   100→/-- E88 multi-head model -/\n   101→structure E88Model (numHeads inputDim headDim : ℕ) where\n   102→  /-- Configuration for each head -/\n   103→  heads : Fin numHeads → E88Head inputDim headDim\n   104→  /-- Output projection from all heads -/\n   105→  outputProj : Matrix (Fin inputDim) (Fin (numHeads * headDim * headDim)) ℝ\n   106→\n   107→/-- Square state matrix for a single head -/\n   108→abbrev HeadState (headDim : ℕ) := Matrix (Fin headDim) (Fin headDim) ℝ\n   109→\n   110→/-- E88 state for all heads -/\n   111→abbrev E88State (numHeads headDim : ℕ) := Fin numHeads → HeadState headDim\n   112→\n   113→/-! ## Part 2: E88 State Update Dynamics -/\n   114→\n   115→/-- Element-wise tanh on matrix -/\n   116→noncomputable def matrixTanh {m n : ℕ} (M : Matrix (Fin m) (Fin n) ℝ) :\n   117→    Matrix (Fin m) (Fin n) ℝ :=\n   118→  Matrix.of fun i j => tanh (M i j)\n   119→\n   120→/-- Outer product: v ⊗ k^T -/\n   121→def outerProduct {m n : ℕ} (v : Fin m → ℝ) (k : Fin n → ℝ) :\n   122→    Matrix (Fin m) (Fin n) ℝ :=\n   123→  Matrix.of fun i j => v i * k j\n   124→\n   125→/-- Sin